		<h2 class="title marb25">The FAST-15 Survey</h2>
		<p>To better understand the foster experience at your organization, we have constructed a survey that you, the foster manager/coordinator, will distribute to your foster caregivers. This survey provides information regarding 1) your fosters’ levels of engagement in your program, and 2) fosters’ feelings, attitudes, and reactions to your program.</p>
		<h2 class="title marb25">Sample Survey Questions</h2>
		<p>To give you an idea of the types of questions that your fosters will be asked about your organization, we have included sample questions from our survey:</p>
		<ul class="bullet">
			<li>I feel appreciated at my organization.</li>
			<li>I am satisfied with the communication I receive from this organization.</li>
			<li>I’m able to rely on other people in my organization when I need extra help.</li>
		</ul>
		<p class="text15">The questions are rated in terms of how much the foster agrees with each statement. The FAST-15 evaluates the health of your foster program on 11 different key areas. To see a list of these key areas, <a href="<?php echo base_url();?>home/submit_org_info" class="linku">click here</a>.</p>
		<p class="text15">There are four main steps in the FAST-15 process. To gain a deeper understanding of the overall process and the time commitment involved, please consult the brief outline provided below:</p>
		<p class="mar0">&nbsp;</p>
