			<div class="steps"><img src="<?php echo base_url();?>asset/images/step01.jpg" alt="Step One" title="Step One" /></div><div class="detail"><h3>Step One:</h3><p>The FAST-15 process will start with a short screener survey which the foster manager can fill out during the application process. The screener survey takes just a few minutes and asks basic questions about your foster program.</p></div><div class="br"></div>
